  "instructions_to_main_agent": [
    "Install 'lucide-react' for icons.",
    "Import Fraunces (serif) and Inter (sans-serif) fonts from Google Fonts.",
    "Build the UI focusing on a warm editorial look, not a generic tech SaaS look. Make sure to use the exact color tokens provided.",
    "Implement Day/Night visual ambiance toggle shifting warm cream to very dark espresso. Use transition-colors duration-1000 for smooth shifting.",
    "Ensure all interactive elements and key information elements have a 'data-testid' attribute in kebab-case."
  ]
